result.adr_address: 33 Wellington St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: AT Bistro

reviews.text: The food is really nice. Environment is cosy. Good for group gatherings. Staff is helpful and nice too. Recommended!!

In Central, if you wanna find something inexpensive for lunch, here for sure is one of the best choices.  There are more than 10 kinds of set lunch for you to choose from and lots of choices of drinks as well, half of them is with no extra charge even.

The portion is not small and delicious and the service is above the standard.  I specially like their tables arrangement, although, it is crowded,  quite a lot of tables for 2 person were set with privacy.  Diners can chat in there with privacy.  It is indeed rare in Central.
It's been my nth time coming to the restaurant.  Surely recommend this place if you are around the area.
Food was delicious and exquisite. Cosy place with balcony for a cigarette.
Good food

result.name: AT Bistro

reviews.text: 樓上東南亞風味餐廳， 食物尚算不錯， 即叫即炒， 只是下午茶餐份量太细少， 像bb餐始的， 如果太肚餓 不建議你叫這個餐， 因為你要叫三個才飽肚喔。
The food is really nice. Environment is cosy. Good for group gatherings. Staff is helpful and nice too. Recommended!!

In Central, if you wanna find something inexpensive for lunch, here for sure is one of the best choices.  There are more than 10 kinds of set lunch for you to choose from and lots of choices of drinks as well, half of them is with no extra charge even.

The portion is not small and delicious and the service is above the standard.  I specially like their tables arrangement, although, it is crowded,  quite a lot of tables for 2 person were set with privacy.  Diners can chat in there with privacy.  It is indeed rare in Central.
Lunch Sets 真係超級勁抵 + 性價比很高。唔明點解中環可以 $120 食到 lunch sets 竟然唔 full house。會繼續支持！

位於13樓的餐廳，面積雖然不大，但佈置很有小酒館的温馨，員工非常友善和健談。中午有set lunch, 可選擇西式或東南亞口味。晚餐供應西式餐點，令人驚喜的是竟然有法式油封鴨腿，而且做得很有水準，這個法國菜式不是普通西餐廳可以供應，可見廚師有一定水準，銀鱈魚也煎得香脆，頭盆有三文魚他他，法式波菜疍餅的皮做得頗薄，餡料亦很美味。甜品亦頗有特色，據說是從法國訂製，有別於一般餐廳的貨色。這裡除提供酒類，還有較少見的手工cider ，味道清甜，非常適合女性。

result.adr_address: Hong Kong, 中環威靈頓街33號, The Loop, 5樓
result.formatted_address: Hong Kong, 中環威靈頓街33號, The Loop, 5樓
result.name: Sagrantino

reviews.text: People who give bad reviews are ordering the wrong things! Their salmon fillet/bruschetta, pastas, lamb, tartara, etc. are all really good.

Simple food at a good price and served relatively fast. Don't expect quality Italian (or to get a seat immediately during a weekday) but the value for money is good if you're around LKF on a budget. Service could be improved, but it's a lunch diner more than a dinner place.
Good Japanese Italian at reasonable prices in Central, early last orders at 9:30
Only the cold pastas are nice here.  The rest are not worth trying.  But the cold pastas (esp tuna and the seafood ones) are tip top.
Nice petite restaurant.  My clam vongole is fresh
